metadata.title: Solution and tools: Is there any example software that can be used to test the solution?

sections.content:
Question:
Is there any example software that can be used to test the solution?
Answer:
The software for the motor control application is delivered as pre-programmed application within the evaluation kit. Please contact your Renesas sales representative or our development partner for more information. 
Suitable Products
RISC-V Voice ASSP
